Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.61,0:00:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.28,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.16,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.93,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.48,0:00:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.99,0:01:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.46,0:01:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.70,0:01:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.07,0:01:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.58,0:01:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個寂寞的男生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得的禮拜天,你都沒地方去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.27,0:01:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.77,0:01:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.47,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很擔心管理員,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟發生了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.18,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒管理員要辭職\N一會兒父母又逼她離開音無家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.62,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也別在這裡發呆鬼混了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快努力加油變成一個\N可以安慰管理員的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.77,0:02:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#25 激鬥!五代對三鷹\N求婚大作戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子狀況很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.19,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然身體還是要動一動\N才會有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.89,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,前些時候\N響子都沒來網球教室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,是有點事\N複雜的家庭問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不需要說出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也沒什麼好隱瞞的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才忘掉煩人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.98,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得讓她清靜一下才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.01,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員是個很容易受傷的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.98,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟你無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是音無小姐的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就跟我有關了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微察覺到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.80,0:03:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她心裡有著很沈重的煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看得出來啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.14,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她打的球出現微妙混亂\N正述說著她心裡的困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網球就是這種運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是亂猜的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在談論些什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問,怎麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.70,0:04:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?難得流了一身大汗\N有沒有覺得很清爽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.71,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能分擔妳一半的煩憂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,光天化日之下\N你在獻什麼殷勤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.88,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊,五代\N你還在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要靠在網子上\N靠到什麼時候啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太難看了啦,年紀輕輕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太不健康了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太沒有男子氣概了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去,我回去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代你也來打網球嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透過鐵網說話真的蠻累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋\N這是主婦的網球教室耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼不通人情嘛\N這也是在做好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像他這種人\N不讓他發洩一下的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會變成性犯罪者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法,我陪你打一局吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?你要跟我打嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你想跟誰打呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練肯定會贏的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒比就知道輸贏的球賽\N太無聊了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來個混合雙打如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙打?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,這是個好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,妳跟我一組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.09,0:05:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了平衡實力\N她應該跟我一組才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?我也要出場嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練還是應該讓一下才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.47,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上的規則你都知道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少懂一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道規則吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.19,0:06:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這個網球教室\N到底在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看過我上場打球嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在輸贏根本無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要管理員的心情\N能夠好起來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.67,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,開心地來動動身體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,努力加油喔,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.85,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.96,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15比0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明有把球打回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一球必須由我來接才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我好像會扯妳後腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,我會幫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.68,0:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方也不懂規則\N這樣說不定會贏喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太\N妳什麼都不用做沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,真不好意思喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一球拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我很閒,我來陪你聊天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.33,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在正被逼迫\N辭掉管理員的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父母希望她能夠再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打進去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你打得很不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他們贏一球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經有再婚對象了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方要發球過來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她是沒有再婚的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先希望她恢復舊姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後跟音無家斷絕關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐上前!五代後退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,一切我都明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.68,0:08:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該考慮到妳父母的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辭掉管理員的工作\N和過去一刀兩斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一輩子和妳同組搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭檔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有聽到剛才那番話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在求婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.79,0:08:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔,年輕人真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪大嬸愛說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.34,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是選擇對象才說的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳選的對象有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.98,0:09:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N根本沒辦法幫管理員排除壓力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在太年輕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱不是忘記了就能解決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,她應該趁這個時候\N考慮再婚的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰再婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都沒有考慮到\N管理員的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這話怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是她這麼做\N完全不是為了跟她爸媽賭氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.71,0:09:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還深愛著惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在很難說出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算我們旁人瞎起\N也沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今天被五代贏了一局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想一輩子\N跟妳同組搭檔的心意依然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.91,0:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,我仔細想過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.89,0:10:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.76,0:10:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你搭檔成為職業網球選手\N我實在辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我真的沒有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是打不倒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹教練來接妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,五代,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N妳該不會是要跟三鷹出去約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭,不是什麼約會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.99,0:12:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是找我出去散散心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要待在那裡,進來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.97,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我們馬上就出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我帶音無小姐出去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢慢玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是三鷹教練吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個是求婚吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一輩子和妳同組搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也覺得那是求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她完全沒聽懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧\N我看她是故意裝糊塗吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.36,0:13:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的,她一定是在裝糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.13,0:13:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來也有這種解讀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果明明知道是求婚\N卻故意裝糊塗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以昨天的答案\N可以當作是N0囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我還有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,上學上學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他住在市中心\N三房兩廳的高級住宅大廈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是資本家的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一流大學畢業\N收入聽說也很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個大帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換作是我的話,就算要甩掉老公\N我都要跟他結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你還在這裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?一大早就悶悶不樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油喔,你還很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕是你唯一的優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一流大學畢業,資本家的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算聽到什麼\N我才不會被嚇到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣可以嗎?\N(紅豆麵包)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時這樣有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望早點畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?當學生比較輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是被當作半大不小的人看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且又沒有財力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠亂花錢的\N也只有當學生的時候喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在吃紅豆麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.15,0:14:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然在我面前吃豬排飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是社會的縮圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我三百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就老實說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就多借兩百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想差不多該去買棟房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要買房子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是住在大廈公寓比較輕鬆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人住是沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要有庭院的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庭院要越大越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在“幾乎看不到邊際”的\N廣大庭院角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,養一隻小狗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你喜歡小狗啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.29,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我尤其喜歡\N像惣一郎那種大型犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布吉,快回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.25,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,好可愛\N真的好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會覺得不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海真的好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想養的狗,只有惣一郎而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白我的意思嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先說清楚\N我不是叫妳把狗讓給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是迂迴地在向妳求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.54,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不知道該怎麼回答你才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解\N不論兩年還是三年我都會等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過了兩三年\N說不定我就不怕狗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.91,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著年輕人大口吃飯\N真的好痛快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是餓壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,葉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.62,0:18:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃,家常菜真的棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你唸什麼科系?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,我唸教育學系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.97,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說將來要當學校的老師囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,這也不見得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是上班族嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作倒是還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望建立一個快樂的家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上絕不在外偷蹓躂\N下了班就直接回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假日一定陪在太太的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.69,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望生兩個孩子,一男一女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.06,0:19:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外在鄉下也好\N我想租個有庭院的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,養一隻狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有著很明確的目標啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.74,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,比起只顧著工作\N完全不顧家的男人好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近的流行風潮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對女人比較幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少小津江比較適合\N居家型的老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,小津江個性比較溫和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊,妳忍受得了貧窮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於持家我可是沒有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能住雙世代住宅就更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.10,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這都要等畢業後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.47,0:19:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,反正還有三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,妳真的很不死心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.22,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因為好奇才問的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去海邊\N聊了一些狗的事情而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有向妳求婚嗎?\N直接明瞭地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,果然求婚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳洗完澡正要回去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說,今天啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,五代,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被她逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也曾經向妳求婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.02,0:20:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸沒向我求婚\N是我叫你爸來跟我求婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是受不了一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的樂趣就只有喝酒\N和聊別人的八卦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這明明不是什麼重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.74,0:20:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的我來說\N不管別人怎麼說我都無法回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果再過些時候\N或許會有所改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過些時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.41,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望妳能再當三年的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.72,0:21:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三…年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,三年以後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來比賽誰先跑回一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.77,0:21:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.67,0:21:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等惣一郎隨著時間流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年以後能怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.77,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了,實在太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.90,0:22:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會認為只要大學畢業\N就能有玫瑰色般的幸福人生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.51,0:22:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況,你三年能畢得了業嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.15,0:22:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說啊,怎麼樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.52,0:22:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會留級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.55,0:22:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會找不到工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算一切順利\N剛畢業的大學生能養得起家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.33,0:22:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在對未來一點概念都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.86,0:22:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.67,0:23:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.08,0:23:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.19,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.26,0:23:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.66,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是五年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳等我五年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.75,0:23:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上因為朋友的來電\N我走下時計坡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.86,0:23:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友閒聊往事\N看著嬰兒的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.96,0:23:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又走回了時計坡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N「五代愕然!響子醋罈大爆發!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天又來到了時計坡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.46,0:24:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.50,0:24:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.34,0:24:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.44,0:24:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.55,0:25:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.29,0:25:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
